{"_path":"/maps/_ai/training/fine-tuning","_dir":"training","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Fine-tuning","description":"Model fine-tuning techniques and best practices","original_path":"_ai/fine-tuning.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"微调-fine-tuning"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"微调 (Fine-tuning)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"axolotlyaml-配置驱动的微调框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Axolotl：YAML 配置驱动的微调框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Axolotl 的核心理念是\"用 YAML 定义整个训练流程\"——从数据预处理、模型加载、训练配置到导出部署，全部收敛在一个配置文件中。这种声明式接口降低了微调门槛，支持 LoRA/QLoRA、全参数微调、多模态微调和持续预训练。2025 年 2 月新增 LoRA 优化，在单 GPU 和多 GPU 训练中进一步降低内存占用并提升训练速度。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/axolotl-ai-cloud/axolotl","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Axolotl GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://docs.axolotl.ai/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Axolotl 官方文档"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"llama-factory一站式-llm-训练与部署平台"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLaMA-Factory：一站式 LLM 训练与部署平台"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLaMA-Factory 是目前最全面的开源微调框架，支持 100+ 模型架构，提供 Web UI 界面让非技术人员也能轻松操作。其特色是集成了模型量化、合并、导出等全流程工具，微调完成后可直接生成 GGUF、vLLM 等部署格式。通过可扩展的模块统一了多种高效微调方法，让大模型微调真正普及。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/hiyouga/LLaMA-Factory","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLaMA-Factory GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/694047673","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLaMA-Factory 使用指南"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"lora低秩适配的参数高效微调"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LoRA：低秩适配的参数高效微调"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LoRA（Low-Rank Adaptation）冻结预训练模型权重，注入可训练的秩分解矩阵到每一层：W = W_0 + BA，其中 W_0 冻结，B 和 A 可训练且秩远小于 W。这种方法将训练参数量减少 10000 倍，同时保持与全参数微调相当的性能，是在消费级 GPU 上微调大模型的标准选择。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2106.09685","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LoRA 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/learn/llm-course/en/chapter11/4","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hugging Face LoRA 教程"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"qlora量化-lora-的极致内存优化"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"QLoRA：量化 + LoRA 的极致内存优化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"QLoRA 将 4-bit 量化与 LoRA 结合，实现最大内存效率。全参数微调 70 亿参数模型需要 100-120GB 显存，而 QLoRA 仅需约 10GB，让消费级 GPU 也能微调大模型。量化后的模型权重以低精度存储，计算时动态反量化，配合 LoRA 的可训练适配器，在效率和效果之间取得完美平衡。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.redhat.com/en/topics/ai/lora-vs-qlora","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LoRA vs QLoRA - RedHat"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.ibm.com/docs/en/watsonx/w-and-w/2.1.0?topic=tuning-qlora-fine","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"IBM QLoRA 文档"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"pefthugging-face-参数高效微调库"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PEFT：Hugging Face 参数高效微调库"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PEFT（Parameter-Efficient Fine-Tuning）是 Hugging Face 开源的参数高效微调库，集成了 LoRA、Prefix Tuning、Prompt Tuning、IA³、Adapter 等多种方法。它让研究者可以用统一接口尝试不同微调策略，无需修改模型代码即可切换方法，极大简化了实验流程。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/huggingface/peft","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PEFT GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/docs/peft/en/conceptual_guides/adapter","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PEFT 方法概览"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"unsloth手写-cuda-内核的极速微调"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Unsloth：手写 CUDA 内核的极速微调"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Unsloth 通过手写 CUDA 内核和算法优化，在保持精度的前提下将微调速度提升 2-5 倍，显存占用降低 50%+。它针对 LLM 训练中的热点操作（RoPE、LayerNorm、Cross-Entropy）定制 CUDA 实现，支持与 PEFT 完全兼容，只需修改几行导入语句即可加速现有 LoRA/QLoRA 训练代码。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://unsloth.ai/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Unsloth 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://unsloth.ai/blog","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Unsloth 博客"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"axolotlyaml-配置驱动的微调框架","depth":2,"text":"Axolotl：YAML 配置驱动的微调框架"},{"id":"llama-factory一站式-llm-训练与部署平台","depth":2,"text":"LLaMA-Factory：一站式 LLM 训练与部署平台"},{"id":"lora低秩适配的参数高效微调","depth":2,"text":"LoRA：低秩适配的参数高效微调"},{"id":"qlora量化-lora-的极致内存优化","depth":2,"text":"QLoRA：量化 + LoRA 的极致内存优化"},{"id":"pefthugging-face-参数高效微调库","depth":2,"text":"PEFT：Hugging Face 参数高效微调库"},{"id":"unsloth手写-cuda-内核的极速微调","depth":2,"text":"Unsloth：手写 CUDA 内核的极速微调"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:training:fine-tuning.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/training/fine-tuning.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/training/fine-tuning","_extension":"md"}